name: hc
descriptionEnglish:
The Hyper Pay is globalization of electronic currency and encrypted digital currency payment solution polymerization, support a variety of mainstream digital currency and electronic real-time seamless exchange and trading legal tender to Pay(includes BTC , ETH, Hcash).

The upcoming implementation includes alipay, WeChat, unionpay, Visa, Mastercard and other existing mainstream electronic currency payment methods.

On November 9, 2017, Hyperpay entered into an agreement with Australia's SUTTONS UGG brand, announcing that it will accept Hcash / Hyperpay as the payment currency for Hyperpay as its smart payment channel.
